      <title>大亨米斯特里的公司获得投资者保证以延期偿还债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/tycoon-mistry-s-firm-gets-investor-assurance-to-defer-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该公司一位高层官员透露，印度 Shapoorji Pallonji 集团已获得全球私人信贷机构的保证，该集团将推迟偿还其子公司 1430 亿卢比（17 亿美元）的部分债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/tycoon-mistry-s-firm-gets-investor-assurance-to-defer-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 02:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FashionValet 创始人因主权财富基金亏损而受到指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/fashionvalet-founders-charged-after-sovereign-wealth-fund-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚检察官对当地一家在线时尚零售商的创始人提出指控，指控两家与政府有关联的公司滥用其公司投资的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/fashionvalet-founders-charged-after-sovereign-wealth-fund-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 01:59:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁 Poonawalla 的贷款机构将增加一倍员工以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/billionaire-poonawalla-s-lender-to-double-staff-in-growth-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度影子银行 Poonawalla Fincorp Ltd. 扩展到新的产品线，并计划在未来五年内将资产增加至 1.5 万亿卢比（177 亿美元），因此该公司计划将员工人数增加一倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/billionaire-poonawalla-s-lender-to-double-staff-in-growth-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 01:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行股上涨，新加坡股市基准创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/singapore-stock-benchmark-headed-for-record-high-as-banks-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对新加坡银行的乐观情绪重燃，推动了整体市场的上涨，新加坡股市有望创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/singapore-stock-benchmark-headed-for-record-high-as-banks-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 01:35:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命 SEC 官员支持加密货币，比特币价格逼近 10 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/bitcoin-btc-nears-record-100-000-on-trump-s-pick-of-atkins-for-sec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普选择一位加密货币支持者担任下一任美国证券监管机构负责人，此举将比特币价格推高至接近 10 万美元的创纪录水平，交易员们对放松监管的前景感到兴奋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/bitcoin-btc-nears-record-100-000-on-trump-s-pick-of-atkins-for-sec</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 01:17:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>火箭实验室的商业展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/rocket-lab-on-business-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rocket Lab 创始人兼首席执行官 Peter Beck 讨论了他对公司增长和业务战略的展望，因为随着当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划提名金融科技亿万富翁贾里德·艾萨克曼为下一任 NASA 局长，太空业务政策将变得更加令人鼓舞。他在“彭博社：亚洲贸易”节目中与 Haidi Stroud-Watts 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/rocket-lab-on-business-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 00:59:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
