      <title>鲍威尔表示谨慎降息后黄金价格保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gold-xauusd-steady-after-powell-flags-cautious-approach-to-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场在可能影响央行下次利率决定的数据公布之前消化了美联储主席的讲话，黄金价格在小幅上涨后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/gold-xauusd-steady-after-powell-flags-cautious-approach-to-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 00:29:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金让 MicroStrategy 成为华尔街最热门的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/convertible-bond-arbs-are-making-microstrategy-wall-street-s-hottest-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了满足自己对比特币数十亿美元的狂热需求，迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 已经利用了散户投资者的需求，这些投资者对 MicroStrategy Inc. 今年超过 500% 的涨幅十分着迷。他还从对冲基金那里获益，这些基金对股票交易地点的关注度要低得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/convertible-bond-arbs-are-making-microstrategy-wall-street-s-hottest-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商将焦点转向 OPEC+ 供应会议，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在下跌后企稳，交易员们期待周四举行的 OPEC+ 会议，预计该组织将再次推迟在供应已经充足的市场中恢复产量的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 23:34:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
